reviewText: My 2 year old son loves these  DVDs. He's a fan of all of these shows and my husband and I can put this on repeat and my son stays entertained. I haven't watched it- just listened- but I definitely appprove of the lessons/values in the episodes. It has Barney, Angelina Ballerina, Bob the  Builder, Fireman Sam, Kipper, Thomas & Friends,and 1 or 2 others.
